snippet.title: Warpitout
snippet.description:
(1982) This is an example of early computer graphics animation developed by students at the Electronic Visualization Lab. This video was created by Jane Veeder.

More information can be found on the EVL website -- http://www.evl.uic.edu/core.php?mod=4&type=5&indi=169
